data.description: Escape to the tranquility of country living in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath country home located in Grand Bay AL. Nestled in the heart of Grand Bay, this property exudes a warm and inviting charm that captures the essence of rural life. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by the picturesque sight of a classic farmhouse-style design, complete with a welcoming front porch, perfect for enjoying a morning cup of coffee or watching the sunset. The exterior boasts traditional elements. Step inside, and you'll find a cozy and comfortable interior with rustic details. The open and airy living room features exposed wooden beams and wooden accent wall. It's the ideal space for family gatherings, relaxation, or curling up with a good book.  Outside, the property is surrounded by woods and privacy fencing. The wide, open spaces offer plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh country air. This country home is a haven for those seeking a slower pace of life, the beauty of nature, and the character of a classic rural property. Whether you're looking for a full-time residence or a weekend getaway, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath country home embodies the quintessential charm of country living. Schedule a visit and experience it for yourself!
